**[1846, 01-20] Ms.A.1.2.16.6**

Sarah Pugh to EPN; Philadelphia

Grateful for note; news of friends; Mary Grew; Abby Kelley’s wedding;
Cassius M. Clay.

“To have such evidence as thy letters give that a true heart, tho’
distant, is beating in union with ours, in the struggle for humanity, is
cheering and strengthening.”


